      <div type="commentary">
        <p n="6">Sampath fn4: vaikal means daily.</p>
        <!--Update!-->
        <p n="7">IP: …[ka]ṟ ūṭṭuvār. Fn4: “This word, not fully read, obviously stands for an administrative or supervisory body like varigar.” --- Sampath fn5: aṭṭuvar = camaippar.</p>
